<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa hehpihna Isu Krista chuh en un,
 Ei venna leh ei hehpihna chuh;
 Chitin namtin in pakchau a lungsietna lien,
 Amah pakchau mi lungsiet pa chuh.

[V2]
 A tatna lopi ziekin Amah pakchai tiu,
 A phatna leh a chitna phuong un;
 Chitin namtin inpakchau a lungsietna lien,
 Amah pakchau mi lungsiet pa chuh.

[V3]
 2. A lungsietna lien tak mai pakcha'n lasai tiu,
 Mi gilo tan dinga hungkum chuh;
 Lalpa Pathien bangkim hihthei leh Lal Messiah,
 A Cha Lalmang ei lungsietpa chuh.

[V4]
 3. Lei leh van a Lal, Immanuel chuh en un,
 A vakna chun ei hun sun eng hen;
 Zie eng achun van Kanaan gam chuh zuon hitiu,
 A Lalna gam chuh I tun na'ng un.</lyrics>
<title>LET US PRAISE AND ADORE</title>
<hymn_number>444</hymn_number>
</song>